{"about_the_game":"<i>Risk of Rain meets Noita.</i><br><br><strong>Space Bot</strong> is a strategic roguelite where your environment is fully desctructable, and out to get you. Travel with your friendly spaceship as you hunt for 'GELD' on far away and mysterious planets.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123110/extras/Collecting_Gold_Lighting.gif?t=1668665429\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Procedural Planets</strong> Have a different experience each time you play with procedurally generated levels<br></li><li><strong>Unique Enemies</strong> Fight increasingly difficult and creepy enemies as you rush to escape<br></li><li><strong>Find Upgrades</strong> Increase your stats as your progress through the game. The better you play, the more upgrades you can use!</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123110/extras/Fighting_a_fly.gif?t=1668665429\" /><br><br>The longer you stay on a planet, the more enemies will appear and attack you. Try and get your Geld and get out!<br><br>Space Bot is currently in development by Incinious. Let me know your thoughts and suggestions on twitter @Incinious!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123110/extras/Worms.gif?t=1668665429\" /><br><br><i>Inspiration for this game was drawn from:</i><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>OpenLiero-X<br></li><li>Motherload<br></li><li>Binding of Isaac<br></li><li>Risk of Rain<br></li><li>Terraria<br></li><li>Noita</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Fly Swatter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2123110/c793dd0cc6eb320939cc36907b67493e6b438320.jpg"},{"name":"Bug Spray","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2123110/eda4a8201152a23333a9cfa67178cf4272935aa7.jpg"},{"name":"Arachnophobia","path":"https://cdn.ak